reviewText: They look brand new, thank you.
It was not what I expected from Baby Einstein. It was short and not interesting to the baby.
Iwas so impressed when I received this product. They were all new except one and that was in perfect condition.  Our granddaughter loves the.

My grandson who has special needs is in heaven. He watches these over and over especially Noah's Ark. He is 9 yrs old but is on about a 24 month level! This collection was an awesome choice for him! He is non verbal but he lets us know which parts excite him! Thank You for giving him hours of education and enjoyment!
I used it at christmas for my grandkids, split them up and put them in there stockings, they loved them...

Everyone attempting to sell a 26 disk set by attaching it to this listing is selling illegal Chinese knockoffs. Knowingly or unknowingly, they are against the law.

There is a legitimate Collection 2 Set, but it is not 26 disks.

Google "counterfeit baby einstein" and you will see.

This was purchased as a gift for a first-time mom ----of twins! It's a great gift set andthey will use it for many years.  the seller was very responsive to all of my questions.  The package arrived prompt and as described.
